The Raspberry Pi 3b comes with a Bluetooth device. It is possible to connect directly to the Raspberry Pi with the mobile phone's Bluetooth. 
When Bluetooth and wifi are used at the same time, music playback may not be smooth. （Need a csr 4.0 Bluetooth adapter to connect to a Raspberry Pi?）
